\c 27
\p
\v 1 Zvino shoko raJehovha rakasvika kwandiri richiti:
\v 2 Zvino iwe mwanakomana wemunhu, simudzire Tire mariro;
\v 3 uti kuTire ugere pakupinda pagungwa, achitengeserana nevanhu pazviwi zvakawanda: Anoreva seizvi Ishe Jehovha: Tire, iwe wakati: Ndakaperera pakunaka.
\v 4 Miganhu yako iri mumoyo yemakungwa; vavaki vako vakaperedzera runako rwako.
\v 5 Vakaita mapuranga ako ese nemisipiresi yekuSeniri; vakatora musidhari kubva kuRebhanoni kuti vakuitire mbiru yechikepe.
\v 6 \add Ne\add*miouki yeBhashani vakaita matanda ako ekukwasva nawo; mukunda weVaAsiriya wakaita zvigaro zvako zvepazvikepe nenyanga dzenzou dzinobva kuzviwi zveKitimi.
\v 7 Mucheka wakapfava kwazvo wakarukirwa unobva Egipita ndiwo waiva wakava chifukidzo chako kuva chiratidzo chako, zveruvara rwedenga nezveruvara rwehute kubva kuzviwi zvaErisha zvakava chifukidzo chako.
\p
\v 8 Vagari veSidhoni neArivhadhi vaiva vakwasvi vako; vakachenjera vako, iwe Tire, vaiva mukati mako, vaiva vafambisi vezvikepe zvako.
\v 9 Vatana veGebhari nevakachenjera varo vaiva mukati mako vari vagadziri vemaburi ako; zvikepe zvese zvegungwa nevafambisi vazvo vaiva mauri kuti vatengesarane newe nhumbi dzako dzekutengeserana.
\v 10 VaPerisiya neVaRudhi neVaPuti vaiva muhondo yako, vanakomana vehondo; vaiturikira mukati mako nhovo nenguwani; ivo vakabudisa pachena runako rwako.
\v 11 Varume veArivhadhi pamwe nehondo yako vaiva pamusoro pemasvingo ako kupoteredza, uye mhare dzaiva pashongwe dzako, vakaremberedza nhovo dzavo pamasvingo ako kupoteredza, vakaperedzera runako rwako.
\p
\v 12 Tarishishi raishambadzirana newe nekuda kweuwandu hwefuma yese, vakatsinhanisa nhumbi dzako nesirivha, nedare, netini, nemutobvu.
\v 13 Javhani, Tubhari, neMesheki, ndivo vatengeserani vako, vakatsinhanisa nhumbi dzako nevanhu nemidziyo yendarira.
\v 14 Veimba yaTogarima vakatsinhanisa nhumbi dzako nemabhiza nevatasvi vemabhiza nemahesera.
\v 15 Varume veDhedhani vaiva vatengeserani vako, zviwi zvizhinji zvaiva zvekutengeserana zvemaoko ako, zvakakuvigira nyanga dzenzou nematanda emushuma kuva chipo.
\v 16 Nyika yeSiriya yaishambadzirana newe nokuda kwezvizhinji zvako zvakaitwa namaoko; vakatenga nhumbi dzako namabwe eemaradhi, nomucheka mutema, nezvakarukwa, nomucheka wakaisvonaka, nekorari, namabwe anovaima.
\v 17 Judha nenyika yaIsraeri ndivo vaitengerana newe; vaitenga nhumbi dzako nezviyo zveMiniti, nezvinotapira, nohuchi, namafuta, nebharisami.
\v 18 Dhamasiko raishambadzirana newe richitenga zvizhinji zvako zvakaitwa namaoko, nokuda kwefuma zhinji yamarudzi ese, newaini yeHeribhoni nemvere chena.
\v 19 Nyika dzeVedhani neJavhani dzakatenga nhumbi dzako nechinda; dare rinobwinya, nekasia, nekaramo ndizvo zvakange zviri pakati penhumbi dzako.
\v 20 Dhedhani raikutengesera micheka inokosha yokutasvisa mabhiza nayo.
\v 21 Nyika yeArabhiya namachinda ese enyika yeKedhari ndivo vaitenga pamaoko enyu; makwayana namakondohwe nembudzi ndizvo zvavaitenga kwauri.
\v 22 Vatengesi veShebha neRaama ndivo vaitengerana newe; vaishambadzira nhumbi dzako nezvinonhuhwira zvakaisvonaka, namabwe ese anokosha, negoridhe.
\v 23 Harani neChane neEdheni ivo vatengesi veShebha neAshuri neKirimadhi ndivo vaitengerana newe.
\v 24 Ndivo vaitengerana newe nenhumbi dzakatsaurwa, nenguvo dzemicheka mitema nezvakarukwa, namabhokisi ezvokupfeka zvinokosha, akasungwa namabote, akavezwa nemisidhari, pakati penhumbi dzako.
\v 25 Zvikepe zveTarishishi ndizvo zvaiimba pamusoro pako nokuda kwenhumbi dzako dzekutengeserana, iwe ukazadzwa, ukaitirwa mbiri mumoyo yamakungwa.
\p
\v 26 Vakwasvi vako vakakuisa kumvura zhinji; mhepo yokumabvazuva yakakuputsa mumoyo wamakungwa.
\v 27 Fuma yako, nenhumbi dzako, nezvokutengesa zvako, vafambisi vezvikepe zvako, navarairi vazvo, navagadziri vako panosinirira mvura, navashambadziri venhumbi dzako, navarwi vako vese, vari mukati mako, navanhu vako vazhinji vari mukati mako, zvese zvichawira mumoyo wamakungwa nezuva rokuparadzwa kwako.
\v 28 Mafungu achadengenyeka nomubvumo wokudanidzira kwavarairi vezvikepe zvako.
\v 29 Vese vanobata namatanda okukwasva, ivo vafambisi navarairi vese vapagungwa, vachaburuka pazvikepe zvavo; vachamira pamahombekombe,
\v 30 vachadana namanzwi avo pamusoro pako, vachachema kwazvo; vachikushira guruva pamisoro yavo; vachaumburukira, mumadota;
\v 31 vachazviita maparavara nouparavara nokuda kwako, vachazvisunga zvivuno namasaga, vachikuchema nemweya ine shungu kwazvo nokuchema kukuru.
\v 32 Pakuchema kwavo vachakuitira mariro, vachachema pamisoro pako, vachiti: Ndianiko wakatongofanana neTire, wakaita saiye wakaparadzwa mukati megungwa?
\v 33 Panguva yakaenda nhumbi dzako kumakungwa, wakagutisa vanhu vazhinji; wakafumisa madzimambo enyika nefuma yako zhinji nezvawaitengesa.
\v 34 Panguva yawakaputswa namakungwa mukati memvura zhinji yakadzika, nhumbi dzako navanhu vako vese zvakawira pasi mukati mako.
\v 35 Vese vagere pazviwi vanoshamiswa pamusoro pako, madzimambo avo anotya kwazvo; zviso zvavo zvinodedera.
\v 36 Vatengesi pakati pamarudzi avanhu vanokuridzira muridzo, wava chinhu chinotyisa, haungatongozovipo.
